refentry.refsect1:
&reftitle.description;
public Imagick Imagick::complexImages intcomplex_operator
Performs complex mathematics on an image sequence, treating the first two images as the real and imaginary parts of a complex number, and returns the resulting images.

&reftitle.parameters;


  complex_operator

   The operation to perform. One of the Imagick::COMPLEX_OPERATOR_* constants.
